History
I started playing 4-7k mid February of 2014.

I played until about August the same year, then came back at the end of June of 2015, but didn't play much because my reading was messed up.

I started playing a little bit more of 7k in September, but it was still only a couple times per week.

In late December I started really playing 7k, as I was playing it almost as much as 4k.

I now (written late April 2016) play pretty much every day, mostly 7k, but I still do spend a little time on 4k.
